summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4190 for the improvement of McGraw Street from Bigelow Avenue North, to a point approximately 300 feet east of Bigelow Avenue North; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 49848, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
